import Form from './styles/Form'

const SignIn = () => {
    return (
        <Form method='post'>
            <fieldset>
                <label htmlFor='email'>
                    Email
                    <input type='email' name='email' placeholder='Ваш E-mail' autoComplete='email' />
                </label>
            </fieldset>
        </Form>
    )
}

export default SignIn
